text: Baguashan Tunnel () is a railway tunnel through Baguashan in Taiwan, located between Taichung HSR station and Changhua HSR station. With a route length of 7,357 meters, it is the longest tunnel on Taiwan High Speed Rail. Mileage of Baguashan Tunnel is TK173+021to TK180+378. ==History== *Apr 9, 2001 work begun. *Aug 29,2002 breakthrough. *Jan 5,2007 opened. ==References== *台灣高速鐵路全線隧道一覽表 - 悠遊台灣鐵道 Category:2007 establishments in Taiwan Category:Railway tunnels in Taiwan Category:Transportation in Changhua County Category:Taiwan High Speed Rail Category:Tunnels completed in 2007
